{"type":"message","id":"67913922","parentId":"afb6cad0","timestamp":"2026-04-12T00:47:02.190Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_iocji072liyn_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"f104e888-eaec-44e0-aead-c6c186de343c\",\n  \"agentId\": \"sammy\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:sammy:main\",\n  \"name\": \"SSH Credentials Reminder\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1775954822172,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1775954822172,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"expr\": \"0 10 * * *\",\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"Send a Telegram message to the user 'Wilkie Devs & Design' saying: '🔔 Hey! ¿Ya tienes las credenciales SSH del VPS de Hostinger? Las necesitas para configurar OpenCode en tu OpenClaw. Mándame un mensaje cuando las tengas y seguimos.'\"\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1776006000000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"f104e888-eaec-44e0-aead-c6c186de343c","agentId":"sammy","sessionKey":"agent:sammy:main","name":"SSH Credentials Reminder","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1775954822172,"updatedAtMs":1775954822172,"schedule":{"expr":"0 10 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"America/Bogota"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Send a Telegram message to the user 'Wilkie Devs & Design' saying: '🔔 Hey! ¿Ya tienes las credenciales SSH del VPS de Hostinger? Las necesitas para configurar OpenCode en tu OpenClaw. Mándame un mensaje cuando las tengas y seguimos.'"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1776006000000}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775954822188}}
{"type":"message","id":"47b09ed7","parentId":"67913922","timestamp":"2026-04-12T00:47:06.175Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to remind them via Telegram. I've set up a cron job that will send them a Telegram message tomorrow at 10 AM Colombia time. But wait - this requires having their Telegram user ID to work properly. Let me check if the Telegram channel is properly configured.\n\nActually, since the gateway already has Telegram configured (I saw the bot token earlier), the \"announce\" delivery mode should send to the configured Telegram channel. But I need to make sure the user is reachable via Telegram.\n\nLet me also check - the message might need a `to` field with their username or ID. Actually the delivery.mode=\"announce\" with no `to` should broadcast to all configured channels.\n","thinkingSignature":"2f46ac98e2a5f57fdc56442e093a2315090f67b97355bbda07dc1a403e13bb26"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nListo, ya tengo el recordatorio configurado. ⏰\n\n**Mañana a las 10:00 AM (Colombia)** te mandaré un Telegram recordándote que necesitas las credenciales SSH del VPS de Hostinger.\n\nTambién te recomiendo:\n- Si tienes acceso al panel de Hostinger, puedes configurar un recordatorio ahí directo\n- O si prefieres, mándame un mensaje aquí cuando tengas las credenciales y continuamos con la configuración de OpenCode\n\n¿Algo más en lo que te pueda ayudar mientras tanto?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":451,"output":252,"cacheRead":31008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31711,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775954822192,"responseId":"062a1e86a378f44eac0892691e0806ee"}}
