{"type":"message","id":"0cafe1b0","parentId":"47121432","timestamp":"2026-04-12T00:49:17.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API paths are all returning 404 for opencode.ai. This means the MiniMax API key is NOT an OpenCode API key. They are separate services.\n\nThe user might be confused or mistaken. I need to let them know that the MiniMax API key doesn't work for OpenCode - they need a separate OpenCode API key.\n\nLet me be direct about this.\n","thinkingSignature":"5724a4e28715ef2359e22453850afad827e4ea179af8b05878f408feae972eb5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n⚠️ Parece que hay una confusión. La API key de MiniMax (`sk-cp-sPgdKbqLq4Ms...`) **no es** una key de OpenCode. Son servicios completamente separados.\n\n**Lo que necesitas para OpenCode:**\n1. Crear cuenta en [opencode.ai](https://opencode.ai)\n2. Ir a Settings → API Keys\n3. Copiar tu key que empieza con `sk-...` (diferente formato)\n\nLa key de MiniMax solo te sirve para los modelos `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7` que ya tienes configurados.\n\n**¿Quieres que te ayude a configurar OpenCode cuando tengas tu API key?** Lo único que necesito es que me pases la key de OpenCode y yo actualizo la config y reinicio el gateway."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2609,"output":246,"cacheRead":50432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53287,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775954954344,"responseId":"062a1f0ad4dc062593d32074bed7addd"}}
