{"type":"message","id":"668142af","parentId":"fd2a61d4","timestamp":"2026-04-12T01:08:52.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to fix the critical issues carefully without breaking anything. Let me start with the most critical ones:\n\n1. Secrets hardcoded - need to move to env vars\n2. iframe in blog sanitization - restrict to allowlist\n3. The `any` types - this is a big refactor, need to be careful\n\nLet me start by reading the affected files and making careful fixes. I'll start with the secrets since those are the most critical.\n","thinkingSignature":"9a66b223c97e8296df14a587fc5a4d9085d4c8264a20292e5ae25aa3de96276e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nEntendido. Voy paso a paso, con cuidado. Empiezo por los **3 bloqueantes críticos**.\n\n---\n\n## Paso 1: Secrets hardcodeados\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pnkkcgnxo1si_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":80,"path":"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/backend/supabase-schema.sql"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57371,"output":189,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57624,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775956127751,"responseId":"062a23a021c98cd8d3266354b350afa0"}}
