{"type":"message","id":"46594d0c","parentId":"eccfa940","timestamp":"2026-04-12T01:12:16.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Commit exitoso. Ahora le doy el reporte final con los secrets generados.","thinkingSignature":"a9244e6570cb4a8956979023a136187da8b13525252b997d72c3a190e0da4a70"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nListo. ✅\n\n**Commit hecho:**\n```\nfix(security): remove hardcoded secrets and fix XSS vectors\n4 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)\n```\n\n**Nuevos secrets generados (cámbialos en el VPS ahora):**\n\n```\nBLOG_WEBHOOK_SECRET=a1108af730b7dc565b3d60d50ea3cdef5a3c73d66aeaf40130b07dd1cf6be2ce\nENTERPRISE_SYNC_TOKEN=ef204017cf64e604b9feeecbcd9a42d92d015ad2dd4362e793a556138bb9ffd686a07dd3dd13e2dd\n```\n\n**Pasos para aplicar en producción:**\n\n```bash\n# 1. Agregar al .env.production del backend\necho \"BLOG_WEBHOOK_SECRET=a1108af730b7dc565b3d60d50ea3cdef5a3c73d66aeaf40130b07dd1cf6be2ce\" >> /root/virtual-tryon/backend/.env.production\necho \"ENTERPRISE_SYNC_TOKEN=ef204017cf64e604b9feeecbcd9a42d92d015ad2dd4362e793a556138bb9ffd686a07dd3dd13e2dd\" >> /root/virtual-tryon/backend/.env.production\n\n# 2. Actualizar en la DB de Supabase (production)\n# Ejecutar en Supabase SQL editor:\nUPDATE blog_settings SET webhook_secret = 'a1108af730b7dc565b3d60d50ea3cdef5a3c73d66aeaf40130b07dd1cf6be2ce' WHERE id = 1;\n\n# 3. Reiniciar el backend\ncd /root/virtual-tryon && docker compose -f docker-compose.backend.yml down && docker compose -f docker-compose.backend.yml up -d\n```\n\n¿Quieres que te ayude con algo más antes de continuar?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":227,"output":452,"cacheRead":70912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71591,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775956326629,"responseId":"062a2466df39e677ef37652ef277dc0a"}}
