{"type":"message","id":"26e5c9ff","parentId":"a40d6ddc","timestamp":"2026-04-12T01:14:36.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The status script works. The git status shows pending changes in the sammy workspace files (which is fine - those are Sammy's own files).\n\nThe Mission Control skill is now created. Let me give the user a summary of what was created.","thinkingSignature":"0b131a7a122eb2f6c2c92df200ce567d259b697279e4e79ab4e041e25c87dd4a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **Mission Control creado.** Aquí está lo que incluye:\n\n```\nmission-control/\n├── SKILL.md                    ← Dashboard principal (se activa con \"mission control\")\n├── scripts/\n│   └── status.sh               ← Status checker interactivo\n└── references/\n    └── project-guide.md        ← Guía de referencia del proyecto\n```\n\n**Verificado con el status checker:**\n\n| Componente | Estado |\n|-----------|--------|\n| WebWizard | ✅ Configured |\n| DevGuardian | ✅ Configured |\n| DataAlchemist | ✅ Configured |\n| GrowthPilot | ✅ Configured |\n| ArchitectAI | ✅ Configured |\n| OpenClaw Gateway | ✅ Running |\n| Frontend | ✅ Found |\n| Backend | ✅ Found |\n| WooCommerce | ✅ Found |\n| Supabase | ✅ Found |\n\n**Commits recientes:**\n```\n449aba4 fix(security): remove hardcoded secrets and fix XSS vectors\n6ed607f feat: optimize review logos with webp support...\n8e31ebd feat(redis): improve local resilience...\n```\n\n**Cambios pendientes:** Solo archivos locales de Sammy (AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, etc.) — son propios del workspace, no del proyecto principal.\n\n---\n\n**Para usar Mission Control:**\n\n- Di \"abre mission control\" o \"estado de los agentes\" y yo cargo el skill\n- Puedo delegar tareas a agentes específicos\n- El script `status.sh` da un overview rápido sin needing OpenClaw\n\n¿Qué quieres hacer ahora?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":654,"output":354,"cacheRead":79936,"cacheWrite":0,"