{"type":"message","id":"28042ad8","parentId":"9da09d28","timestamp":"2026-04-12T01:16:11.268Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-11 20:16 GMT-5] como puedo visualizar el mission control?"}],"timestamp":1775956571263}}
{"type":"message","id":"ea4b44e5","parentId":"28042ad8","timestamp":"2026-04-12T01:16:18.322Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how they can visualize or access the Mission Control. Let me think about the options:\n\n1. **Through OpenClaw directly** - I can show the status on demand\n2. **Canvas** - I could create a visual dashboard using the canvas tool\n3. **Browser** - Open the OpenClaw web UI\n4. **CLI** - Run the status.sh script\n\nThe best approach would be to create a visual dashboard using the canvas tool, or show them the OpenClaw web interface. Let me offer a few options.\n\nActually, let me think about the most practical way to \"visualize\" this. The user might want:\n1. A visual dashboard in the browser\n\n\n2. A text-based status in the chat\n3. A standalone HTML page\n\nI could create an HTML dashboard that displays all the agent statuses visually and show it to them through the canvas tool.","thinkingSignature":"6c6048f525696fa8fe68b2ddaef63c42fb313d4fde40ac0ca3693da923804def"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nTienes varias opciones:\n\n### Opción 1: Dashboard Visual (lo creo ahora)\n\nPuedo crear un dashboard HTML visual y mostrarlo en el canvas. Es el más atractivo.\n\n### Opción 2: Status en Chat (ya lo tienes)\n\nPuedo correr el checker ahora mismo y mostrarte el estado en texto formateado.\n\n### Opción 3: Abrir OpenClaw Web UI\n\nAcceder a `http://localhost:18789` o el port que tengas configurado para ver agentes y sessions.\n\n---\n\n**¿Cuál prefieres?**\n\nSi quieres el **dashboard visual**, lo genero al toque y te lo muestro. Sería algo como:\n\n```\n┌────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│       🎛️  MISSION CONTROL — LOOKITRY        │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  ✅ Gateway: Online                        │\n│  ✅ Agentes: 5/5 activos                   │\n│  ✅ Frontend: OK                           │\n│  ✅ Backend: OK                            │\n│  ✅ WooCommerce: OK                        │\n│  ⚠️  Pending: 1 commit sin push           │\n└────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n¿Qué te late más?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":402,"output":430,"cacheRead":80576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81408,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775956571268,"responseId":"062a255be339a957fcf594c758dcec73"}}
