═════════════════════════════[0m\n\n[0;34m─── Agent Workspaces ───[0m\nWebWizard:    [0;32m✓[0m Configured\nDevGuardian:  [0;32m✓[0m Configured\nDataAlchemist:[0;32m✓[0m Configured\nGrowthPilot:  [0;32m✓[0m Configured\nArchitectAI:  [0;32m✓[0m Configured\n\n[0;34m─── OpenClaw Gateway ───[0m\nGateway:      [0;32m✓ Running[0m\n\n[0;34m─── Project Structure ───[0m\nFrontend:     [0;32m✓[0m Found\nBackend:     [0;32m✓[0m Found\nWooCommerce: [0;32m✓[0m Found\nBrain:       [0;32m✓[0m Found\nSupabase:    [0;32m✓[0m Found\n\n[0;34m─── Docker Containers ───[0m\n  [1;33m⚠[0m Docker not available locally\n\n[0;34m─── Recent Commits ───[0m\n449aba4 fix(security): remove hardcoded secrets and fix XSS vectors\n6ed607f feat: optimize review logos with webp support and fix svg loading issues\n8e31ebd feat(redis): improve local resilience and status check for queue worker\ndd2a5c0 fix(sammy): handle MiniMax reasoning_content when content is empty\n3067f99 fix(redis): configure redis connection for production and activate queue worker\n\n[0;34m─── Git Status ───[0m\n[1;33m⚠ Changes pending[0m\n M Lookitry_Brain_Vault/.obsidian/graph.json\n?? sammy/.openclaw/\n?? sammy/AGENTS.md\n?? sammy/BOOTSTRAP.md\n?? sammy/HEARTBEAT.md\n?? sammy/IDENTITY.md\n?? sammy/SOUL.md\n?? sammy/TOOLS.md\n?? sammy/USER.md\n\n[0;34m═══════════════════════════════════════════[0m\n[0;34m     END MISSION CONTROL STATUS[0m\n[0;34m═══════════════════════════════════════════[0m","cwd":"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/sammy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775956688247}}
{"type":"message","id":"60047ab0","parentId":"eead2740","timestamp":"2026-04-12T01:18:55.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The MissionControl project from ndeadly is a Nintendo Switch sysmodule for Bluetooth controllers - it has nothing useful for our mission control dashboard. The key inspiration is that it uses a \"Tesla overlay\" style menu system.\n\nFor our mission control, I'll create a sleek dashboard HTML that I can display on the canvas. Let me build it with a dark theme, agent status cards, system health, and recent activity - something that looks like a real mission control center.\n\nLet me create a beautiful visual dashboard using HTML/CSS/JS that can be displayed on the canvas.\n","thinkingSignature":"ab3f8723110b4a4be79f1e9585160fc40b60735cf88bdb3665c312e540ea90ff"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jh0obat4wzvb_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Mission Control — Lookitry</title>\n  <style>\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n    \n    :root {\n      --bg-primary: #0a0e17;\n      --bg-secondary: #111827;\n      --bg-card: #1a2235;\n      --bg-card-hover: #1f2a40;\n      --accent-cyan: #00d4ff;\n      --accent-green: #00ff88;\n      --accent-yellow: #ffd60a;\n      --accent-red: #ff4757;\n      --accent-purple: #a855f7;\n      --text-primary: #f1f5f9;\n      --text-secondary: #94a3b8;\n      --border-color: #2a3a5c;\n    }\n    \n    body {\n      font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n      background: var(--bg-primary);\n      color: var(--text-primary);\n      min-height: 100vh;\n      background-image: \n        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 0%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),\n        radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 100%, rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);\n    }\n    \n    .container {\n      max-width: 1400px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      padding: 24px;\n    }\n    \n    /* Header */\n    .header {\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n      margin-bottom: 32px;\n      padding-bottom: 24px;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    }\n    \n    .logo {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 16px;\n    }\n    \n    .logo-icon {\n      width: 48px;\n      height: 48px;\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-cyan), var(--accent-purple));\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      font-size: 24px;\n    }\n    \n    .logo-text h1 {\n      font-size: 24px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-cyan), var(--accent-green));\n      -webkit-background-clip: text;\n      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n      background-clip: text;\n    }\n    \n    .logo-text span {\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      letter-spacing: 2px;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n    }\n    \n    .status-badge {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 8px;\n      padding: 8px 16px;\n      background: var(--bg-card);\n      border: 1px solid var(--accent-green);\n      border-radius: 24px;\n      color: var(--accent-green);\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n    }\n    \n    .status-badge::before {\n      content: '';\n      width: 8px;\n      height: 8px;\n      background: var(--accent-green);\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n    }\n    \n    @keyframes pulse {\n      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n      50% { opacity: 0.5; }\n    }\n    \n    /* Grid Layout */\n    .dashboard-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;\n      gap: 24px;\n    }\n    \n    /* Cards */\n    .card {\n      background: var(--bg-card);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n      border-radius: 16px;\n      padding: 20px;\n      transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    \n    .card:hover {\n      background: var(--bg-card-hover);\n      border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);\n    }\n    \n    .card-header {\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n    \n    .card-title {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 1px;\n    }\n    \n    /* Agent Cards */\n    .agents-section {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n    \n    .agent-card {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 16px;\n      padding: 16px;\n      background: var(--bg-secondary);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    \n    .agent-card:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent-cyan);\n      transform: translateX(4px);\n    }\n    \n    .agent-avatar {\n      width: 48px;\n      height: 48px;\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      font-size: 20px;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n    \n    .agent-avatar.webwizard { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2); }\n    .agent-avatar.devguardian { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb, #f5576c); }\n    .agent-avatar.dataalchemist { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe, #00f2fe); }\n    .agent-avatar.growthpilot { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43e97b, #38f9d7); }\n    .agent-avatar.architectai { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fa709a, #fee140); }\n    \n    .agent-info {\n      flex: 1;\n    }\n    \n    .agent-name {\n      font-size: 15px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n    \n    .agent-specialty {\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n    }\n    \n    .agent-status {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 6px;\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: var(--accent-green);\n    }\n    \n    .agent-status::before {\n      content: '';\n      width: 6px;\n      height: 6px;\n      background: currentColor;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n    }\n    \n    .agent-arrow {\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      font-size: 18px;\n    }\n    \n    /* Stats Cards */\n    .stats-row {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n      gap: 16px;\n      margin-bottom: 24px;\n    }\n    \n    .stat-card {\n      padding: 20px;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    \n    .stat-icon {\n      font-size: 24px;\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n    \n    .stat-value {\n      font-size: 28px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n    \n    .stat-label {\n      font-size: 11px;\n      color: var(--text-secondary);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 1px;\n    }\n    \n    .stat-card.green .stat-value { color: var(--accent-green); }\n    .stat-card.cyan .stat-value { color: var(--accent-cyan); }\n    .stat-card.yellow .stat-value { color: var(--accent-yellow); }\n    .stat-card.purple .stat-value { color: var(--accent-purple); }\n    \n    /* Recent Activity */\n    .activity-list {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n    \n    .activity-item {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n      gap: 12px;\n      padding: 12px;\n      background: var(--bg-secondary);\n      border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    \n    .activity-dot {\n      width: 8px;\n      height: 8px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      margin-top: 6px;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n    \n    .activity-dot.commit { background: var(--accent-green); }\n    .activity-dot.alert { background: var(--accent-red); }\n    .activity-dot.update { background: var(-