{"type":"message","id":"e844cb01","parentId":"aa91916b","timestamp":"2026-04-12T01:19:37.609Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Port 18792 is already in use (OpenClaw uses it). Let me try a different port and also check if I can use the existing OpenClaw web server.\n","thinkingSignature":"7a693c6d2a661761abd1c9b718efd4602a988f3d4522fd8d08c39d3ecdaa3842"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nEl dashboard Mission Control está listo. 🎛️\n\nEl archivo está en: `file:///home/travis/.openclaw/canvas/mission-control.html`\n\n**Tienes 3 formas de verlo:**\n\n1. **Abrir directamente en tu browser:**\n   ```\n   file:///home/travis/.openclaw/canvas/mission-control.html\n   ```\n\n2. **Si el canvas de OpenClaw está funcionando**, puedo mostrarlo ahí.\n\n3. **Con un servidor local temporal:**\n   ```bash\n   cd /home/travis/.openclaw/canvas && python3 -m http.server 18793\n   ```\n   Luego abrir `http://localhost:18793/mission-control.html`\n\n---\n\n**Lo que incluye el dashboard visual:**\n\n| Sección | Contenido |\n|---------|-----------|\n| 🎛️ **Header** | Logo + \"ALL SYSTEMS OPERATIONAL\" badge |\n| 📊 **Stats** | 5 agents, 6 commits, 4 services, 1 pending |\n| 🤖 **Agent Roster** | 5 cards interactivas (WebWizard, DevGuardian, DataAlchemist, GrowthPilot, ArchitectAI) |\n| 🏥 **Project Health** | 8 items (Frontend, Backend, Woo, DB, Docker, Security, Payments, Email) |\n| ⚡ **Quick Actions** | Full Audit, Deploy, Run Tests, Analytics |\n| 📝 **Recent Commits** | Últimos 4 commits |\n| 📡 **Activity Feed** | Feed de actividad |\n\n¿Quieres que lo abra en el canvas o prefieres verlo de otra forma?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":406,"output":364,"cacheRead":91296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92066,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775956770766,"responseId":"062a262342cfdbc7f0288bda4b19fdb9"}}
