{"type":"message","id":"46c8af0d","parentId":"8e54b499","timestamp":"2026-04-12T02:24:15.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I created a symlink. Now let me create a PROJECT.md file in Rebecca's workspace that explains what the Lookitry project is and how to access it.","thinkingSignature":"1d482f1bbb8caa4461e7d29330c3c2fc9e186556c8d3774374d4c2190ad0bbb9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cqxidc0w6dz1_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/travis/.openclaw/workspaces/rebecca/PROJECT.md","content":"# Lookitry Project Reference\n\n## Project Overview\nLookitry es un SaaS de **Virtual Try-On** (probador virtual de ropa) que permite a usuarios probarse ropa virtualmente usando IA.\n\n## Project Structure\n```\nLookitry/\n├── frontend/              # Next.js 14 (App Router)\n├── backend/              # Express + TypeScript\n├── lookitry-woocommerce/ # Plugin WordPress/WooCommerce\n├── supabase/             # Schema de base de datos\n└── brain/               # Lookitry Brain Vault\n```\n\n## Quick Access\n- **Project root:** `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry`\n- **Frontend:** `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/frontend`\n- **Backend:** `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/backend`\n- **Brain Vault:** `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/Lookitry_Brain_Vault/Cerebro`\n\n## Key Files\n- `REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md` — Reglas del proyecto\n- `MAPA_MAESTRO.md` — Mapa general\n- `PRD.md` — Product Requirements Document\n- `TECH_STACK.md` — Tech stack completo\n\n## Communication with Sammy\nPara comunicarte con Sammy, usa:\n```\nsessions_send(sessionKey=\"agent:sammy:main\", message=\"...\")\n```\n\n## Main Technologies\n- **Frontend:** Next.js 14, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion, TypeScript\n- **Backend:** Express, TypeScript, Supabase, Redis, n8n\n- **Payments:** Wompi, PayPal\n- **Email:** Brevo\n- **Storage:** MinIO (S3-compatible)\n- **Deployment:** Docker, Traefik, VPS Hostinger\n\n## Important Notes\n- Secrets están en `.env.production` del VPS\n- No hacer push de API keys o secrets\n- Consultar `REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md` antes de procesar pedidos sensibles\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114202,"output":505,"cacheRead":14507,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129214,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775960644086,"responseId":"062a3544875e515ef4d2b0ef58ad53d7"}}
