{"type":"message","id":"e3e3224c","parentId":"d6135161","timestamp":"2026-04-12T02:24:41.431Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create a shared inbox coordination file that Rebecca, Leo, and I can all access.","thinkingSignature":"a4ffe8d9949a2d6a49af0469e2a39607e16625a09bf76b6d8f95147e143ab2fe"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z5rkqajjydwo_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/.shared-inbox/INBOX.md","content":"# 📬 Shared Inbox — Lookitry Coordination\n\nEste folder es el punto de coordinación central entre Sammy, Rebecca, y Leo.\n\n## Cómo funciona\n\n1. **Cuando necesites algo** de otro agente, crea un archivo aquí\n2. **El receptor revisa** este folder periódicamente\n3. **完成标记** — Cuando termines, marca como done o elimina\n\n## Formato de mensajes\n\n```\nDE: [rebecca|leo|sammy]\nPARA: [rebecca|leo|sammy]\nTIPO: [task|question|update|approval]\nURGENTE: [true|false]\n---\nTÍTULO: [breve descripción]\nCONTENIDO: [detalle completo]\n---\nRECIBIDO: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM\nSTATUS: [pending|in-progress|done|blocked]\n```\n\n## Archivos activos\n\n(No hay mensajes pendientes por ahora)\n\n## Referencias\n\n- **Sammy** (orchestrator): `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/sammy/`\n- **Rebecca** (embajadora): `/home/travis/.openclaw/workspaces/rebecca/`\n- **Leo** (colaborador): `/home/travis/.openclaw/workspaces/leo/`\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":116766,"output":336,"cacheRead":14507,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131609,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775960670027,"responseId":"062a355ed20459d4141e42cca33a7ec1"}}
